Sapporo Snow Festival is one of the largest winter festivals in Japan.
If you want to eat delicious ramen, you should go to Ramen Kyowakoku.
Sapporo Snow Festival has three sites.
The largest one is Odori Park, in Chuo-ku.
Next one is Tsudome, in Higashi-ku.
Another one is Susukino Street near Odori.
Ramen Kyowakoku is near Sapporo Station.
It is a five-minute walk from the station.
